This repo contains DFModel to model DL performance on modern accelerators.

How to use:
1. Set up your csv file for kernels/buffers/system in a directory in the current folder (name the folder after the DL model name).
2. Run "protoc --python_out=. dataflow_graph.proto" to generate protobuf file for dataflow graph class.
3. Run "python create_dataflow_graph_in_pb.py --name=GPT3_175B" to generate protobuf binary and text file in your folder.
4. Run "python visualize_dataflow_graph_in_pydot.py --name=GPT3_175B" to generate pydot graph file in your folder.

